965static uint16_T look1_iu16lu64n48_binlcse(uint16_T u0, const uint16_T bp0[],



966  const uint16_T table[], uint32_T maxIndex)



967{



968  uint16_T y;



969  uint64_T frac;



970  uint32_T iRght;



971  uint32_T iLeft;



972  uint32_T bpIdx;



973



974  /* Lookup 1-D



975     Search method: 'binary'



976     Use previous index: 'off'



977     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



978     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



979     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



980     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



981     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



982   */



983  /* Prelookup - Index and Fraction



984     Index Search method: 'binary'



985     Extrapolation method: 'Clip'



986     Use previous index: 'off'



987     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



988     Remove protection against out-of-range input in generated code: 'off'



989     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



990   */



991  if (u0 <= bp0[0U]) {



992    iLeft = 0U;



993    frac = 0ULL;



994  } else if (u0 < bp0[maxIndex]) {



995    /* Binary Search */



996    bpIdx = maxIndex >> 1U;



997    iLeft = 0U;



998    iRght = maxIndex;



999    while (iRght - iLeft > 1U) {



1000      if (u0 < bp0[bpIdx]) {



1001        iRght = bpIdx;



1002      } else {



1003        iLeft = bpIdx;



1004      }



1005



1006      bpIdx = (iRght + iLeft) >> 1U;



1007    }



1008



1009    frac = ((uint64_T)(uint16_T)((uint32_T)u0 - bp0[iLeft]) << 48) / (uint16_T)



1010      ((uint32_T)bp0[iLeft + 1U] - bp0[iLeft]);



1011  } else {



1012    iLeft = maxIndex - 1U;



1013    frac = 281474976710656ULL;



1014  }



1015



1016  /* Interpolation 1-D



1017     Interpolation method: 'Linear point-slope'



1018     Use last breakpoint for index at or above upper limit: 'off'



1019     Rounding mode: 'simplest'



1020     Overflow mode: 'wrapping'



1021   */



1022  if (table[iLeft + 1U] >= table[iLeft]) {



1023    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)(uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft + 1U]



1024      - table[iLeft]) * frac) >> 48) + table[iLeft]);



1025  } else {



1026    y = (uint16_T)((uint32_T)table[iLeft] - (uint16_T)(((uint16_T)((uint32_T)



1027      table[iLeft] - table[iLeft + 1U]) * frac) >> 48));



1028  }



1029



1030  return y;



1031}

2269  real_T rtb_Sum_c;



2270  real_T rtb_Saturate;



2271  uint32_T MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8ACT;



2272  real_T Integrator;



2273  if (localDW->MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8A_e) {



2274    MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8ACT = 0U;



2275  } else {



2276    MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8ACT = rtM->Timing.clockTick1 -



2277      localDW->MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8A_k;



2278  }



2279



2280  localDW->MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8A_k = rtM->Timing.clockTick1;



2281  localDW->MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8A_e = false;



2282



2283  /* Sum: '<S70>/Sum1' */



2284  rtb_Sum1_b = rtu_slipTarget - rtu_currentSlip;



2285



2286  /* DiscreteIntegrator: '<S80>/Integrator' */



2287  if (localDW->Integrator_SYSTEM_ENABLE != 0) {



2288    Integrator = localDW->Integrator_DSTATE;



2289  } else if ((rtu_reset > 0.0) && (localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState <= 0)) {



2290    localDW->Integrator_DSTATE = 0.0;



2291    Integrator = localDW->Integrator_DSTATE;



2292  } else {



2293    Integrator = 0.001 * (real_T)MODESACCELERATION_PIDLAUNCH8ACT *



2294      localDW->Integrator_PREV_U + localDW->Integrator_DSTATE;



2295  }



2296



2297  /* End of DiscreteIntegrator: '<S80>/Integrator' */



2298



2299  /* Sum: '<S80>/Sum' incorporates:



2300   *  Gain: '<S80>/Proportional Gain'



2301   */



2302  rtb_Sum_c = -0.320404828549429 * rtb_Sum1_b + Integrator;



2303



2304  /* Saturate: '<S80>/Saturate' */



2305  if (rtb_Sum_c > 0.0) {



2306    rtb_Saturate = 0.0;



2307  } else if (rtb_Sum_c < -35.0) {



2308    rtb_Saturate = -35.0;



2309  } else {



2310    rtb_Saturate = rtb_Sum_c;



2311  }



2312



2313  /* End of Saturate: '<S80>/Saturate' */



2314



2315  /* Sum: '<S70>/Sum' incorporates:



2316   *  Constant: '<S70>/Constant1'



2317   */



2318  *rty_clutchVal = rtb_Saturate + 40.0;



2319



2320  /* Sum: '<S70>/Minus' incorporates:



2321   *  Constant: '<S70>/Constant'



2322   *  Constant: '<S70>/Constant2'



2323   *  DataTypeConversion: '<S70>/Cast'



2324   *  Product: '<S70>/Multiply'



2325   */



2326  localDW->Minus = (uint16_T)(2000 - (uint16_T)(20.0 * *rty_clutchVal));



2327



2328  /* S-Function (ClutchMotor_setPWMRegister): '<S70>/ClutchMotor SetPWMRegister' */



2329  ClutchMotor_setPWMRegister_Outputs_wrapper(&localDW->Minus);



2330



2331  /* Update for DiscreteIntegrator: '<S80>/Integrator' incorporates:



2332   *  Gain: '<S80>/Integral Gain'



2333   *  Sum: '<S80>/SumI1'



2334   *  Sum: '<S80>/SumI2'



2335   */



2336  localDW->Integrator_SYSTEM_ENABLE = 0U;



2337  localDW->Integrator_DSTATE = Integrator;



2338  if (rtu_reset > 0.0) {



2339    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = 1;



2340  } else if (rtu_reset < 0.0) {



2341    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = -1;



2342  } else if (rtu_reset == 0.0) {



2343    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = 0;



2344  } else {



2345    localDW->Integrator_PrevResetState = 2;



2346  }



2347



2348  localDW->Integrator_PREV_U = -4.31202961744973 * rtb_Sum1_b + (rtb_Saturate -



2349    rtb_Sum_c);



2350



2351  /* End of Update for DiscreteIntegrator: '<S80>/Integrator' */



2352}

2399static int32_T Gearshift_getTime(void)



2400{



2401  int32_T time;

2410      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)NT_CLUTCH_DELAY];

2415        break;

2419        break;

2421       case 3:

2423        break;

2427        break;

2431        break;



2432      }



2433    }



2434  } else if (rtDW.is_UPSHIFTING == IN_UP_REBOUND) {



2435    if (rtDW.is_NEUTRAL_STATE == IN_SET_NEUTRAL) {

2437    } else {

2439    }

2443    } else {



2444      time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)UP_BRAKE];



2445    }



2446  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_START) {



2447    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)CLUTCH];



2448  } else if (rtDW.is_DOWNSHIFTING == IN_DOWN_PUSH) {

2451    time = rtDW.UnitDelay1[(int32_T)DN_REBOUND];



2452  } else {

2456  return time;



2457}

2796static void checkShift(void)



2797{



2798  int32_T b_previousEvent;



2799  if (rtDW.RateTransition2[0] != rtDW.lastShiftCom) {



2800    rtDW.lastShiftCom = rtDW.RateTransition2[0];



2801    if (rtDW.RateTransition2[1] == GEAR_COMMAND_UP) {



2802      b_previousEvent = rtDW.sfEvent;



2803      rtDW.sfEvent = event_GearshiftUp;



2804      if (rtDW.is_active_NEUTRAL_STATE != 0U) {



2805        NEUTRAL_STATE();



2806      }



2807

2809      if (rtDW.is_active_GEARSHIFT != 0U) {



2810        GEARSHIFT();



2811      }
